Disadvantages of without use of method : 
     1. retype same code again - reusablity less
     2. Readablity of code decrease
     3. Not easy to done modification
     4. Code length increase

Advantages of method : 
     1. Reusablity increase
     2. Code length reduce
     3. Easily modify
     4. Readablity increase

What is Method :
   Method -> block of code, collections of statements, set of code group together to perform some operation or task.
   
   => method signature
   
Task : Bank - class - user details method
       operation in bank - opening an account  ( save details ) 
                         - credit card 
                         
       